items.name: Air-Pollution-Prediction-System-Using-Data-Mining-Technique
items.description: This project combines IoT air quality monitoring and machine learning for AQI forecasting. An IoT device with Arduino Uno and sensors monitors CO, SO2, NO2, O3, PM2.5, and PM10, transmitting data via NodeMCU to MongoDB. CPCB data enhances insights. Models like ARIMA, SARIMA, Prophet, and LSTM were tested, with Prophet best for AQI prediction.
